Package: lernstick-libreoffice-gtk
Architecture: all
Depends: libreoffice-gtk
Description: Enforce GNOME user interface
 We enforce the GNOME user interface because the file dialog in the KDE
 user interface currently just sucks.
 See https://bugs.debian.org/cgi-bin/bugreport.cgi?bug=752230 for details.
 We also add a workaround for the following bug:
 https://bugs.debian.org/cgi-bin/bugreport.cgi?bug=798591
